7. **Keyboard (digest result):**  
   - **DEX rows:** Only `https://` `url=` from `build_personalized_trading_dex_keyboard`
     (pair-aware Ubeswap / Uniswap / Jumper + other venue links). **Two** `url=`
     buttons per row (approved layout).  
   - **Optional on-ramp row (stablecoins in Groq suggestions or resolved swap pair):**
     `https://` `url=` from `build_onramp_keyboard_rows`: **Transak** and **Ramp** only
     if `TRANSAK_API_KEY` / `RAMP_HOST_API_KEY` are set; **Celo on-ramps (directory)**
     → `https://docs.celo.org/home/ramps` when this row is shown. **Max 3** `url=`
     buttons in that row (§4). Optional `walletAddress` / `userAddress` prefill from
     `db.get_wallet` when the user has registered a wallet.  
   - **Final row only:** `callback_data` **⬅️ Back** (`back:{digest_id}`). **Never** put
     `url=` and `callback_data=` on the same row (§4).
8. **Send flags:** `parse_mode=ParseMode.HTML`, `disable_web_page_preview=True` on the
   result message.

